Bates, 1889, males from CMNC (label data: 52 &quot;Guatemala, Zacapa / rd. to San Lorenzo, 4200' / June 10-15, 1991 / E. Giesbert, coll.&quot; 53 &quot;GUAT. Baja Verapaz / 14.5km N.
